{
  "stem": "4963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were picking up bricks and-- with mortar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so-- and some of the women were cooking, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] baking and-- and-- for the, you know, for the Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went back into the workforce and managed to get back into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember distinctly my Aunt Paula starting to shake me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What kind-- [SPEAKING GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What kind of a child are you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't you realize the danger that--?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they-- they told-- they told you they will keep you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stay there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, no, the few things that I had left from my parents were very, very important to me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so it was pictures and a-- a necklace that I had from my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the necklace that I had from my mother, I don't think it was gold-plated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still have it to this day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I said, well don't worry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember my aunt really picking me up-- my Aunt Paula picking me up by my shoulders and starting to-- to actually jerk me and saying, what?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't you understand?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll go out tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll-- I'm fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll just take the few things, and I'll leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I did that and, you know, said goodbye to them because before I didn't really say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And left the next morning, repeated the whole process and went in there, went to these people's home and they told me right away that people had-- that they had rumors.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was actually-- [INAUDIBLE] was a small suburb, and even though our house was very modern and-- to this day, and-- in the back, right the next street they were living primitive lives.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
